      <p style="color:#B2F5EA;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.8;margin:0 0 12px;">
        Index is a specialist service provider, focusing on police clearance certificates and other international individual and business services. With 25+ years of expertise in this industry, we have gained considerable knowledge and insight on delivering professional and timely police clearance certificates.
